  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ハドソンのパズルアクション。金塊を集めて脱出せよ。ステージエディット機能付き。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "This updated take on the original Lode Runner is essentially an entirely new game, but it keeps the core of Douglas Smith's original ideas intact.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "videojuego de 2007",
